as the solar cycle evolves. Analysis of further SDO/AIA CBP data will\nalso help in better understanding of the temporal behaviour of the rotation\nvelocity residuals, meridional motions and Reynolds stress.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Jan 2016 11:32:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-17"}
